name: Tiger Series: Khan
additionalNotes:
There are four different types of wrapper shades present on the Black Label Trading Company Shere Khan, dark, medium and light brown along with Candela. Candela covers the foot and the head is finished off with six caps of varying color and a long pigtail that is tightly curled into a bun. There is no band on the cigar.
